    "feat": {
        "name": "Frightful Attrition",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Your diminishment of your foes' ranks damages their morale. Whenever you reduce a creature to 0 HP with a Strike or spell, all enemies within 30 feet of the downed creature who witnessed the attack must attempt a Will saving throw against your class DC. A creature that didn't see you directly (such as if you're invisible or remained hidden after the attack) takes a \u20132 circumstance penalty to this save. Regardless of the result, each creature is temporarily immune to your Frightful Attrition for 10 minutes.",
